primary.request: Register a new account on the website
primary.context: Caller received a message saying their ownership type requires special handling for registration
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller using a contract ID and name, then sent a Clubhouse registration link via email.

steps: Caller requested help with website registration.
Agent attempted lookup by phone number which failed.
Agent performed successful lookup using contract ID.
Agent verified identity after initial name mismatch (caller provided parent's name).
Agent confirmed contact details and sent registration link via email.
Caller confirmed this was what they needed.

clarifications.note: Agent clarifying if registration or password reset
Agent asking to spell name for verification

corrections.note: Caller explains multiple names on contract after mismatch

actions.detail: Lookup by Brazilian phone number returned no match
Verified using secondary name on contract and state
Sent registration link to email on file

insights.summary: The caller wanted to register for the new website after seeing a 'special handling' error. The agent successfully looked up the account via contract ID and sent a registration link to the email on file.
insights.verbatim: Perfect. So I have to log in in Vacatia, the new website.
